"interpreter <whatsnew314-tail-call-interpreter>` with all optimizations "
"enabled. The speedups for JIT builds versus no JIT builds range from roughly "
"15% slowdown to over 100% speedup (ignoring the ``unpack_sequence`` "
"microbenchmark) on x86-64 Linux and AArch64 macOS systems."
